OL,3,CWhat is the role of the King on
OL,4,Cresults day?
OL,6,F"You must be absolutely exhausted,"
OL,7,Fthe King said to Keir Starmer in the
OL,8,Fmeeting that officially appointed him
OL,9,Fas the new prime minister
OL,11,FThere was once a time when British
OL,12,FMonarchs had absolute power.
OL,14,FBut in our parliamentary democracy,
OL,15,FKing Charles, like Queen Elizabeth
OL,16,Fbefore him, has very few prerogative
OL,17,Fpowers left - most of them having been
OL,18,Fabolished or placed elsewhere with
OL,19,Fministers.
