OL,3,CWhat is the role of the King on
OL,4,Cresults day?
OL,6,FThey arrived in the quadrangle of the
OL,7,Fpalace and meet the Monarch in the
OL,8,Fprivate audience room, before Sunak
OL,9,Fdeparted by the back door (usually the
OL,10,Fgarden exit) to preserve some dignity.
OL,12,FThe King then invited Starmer to
OL,13,Fattend Buckingham Palace and asked him
OL,14,Fto form the new government.
OL,16,FJust before his arrival certain
OL,17,Fexecutive powers are vested in the
OL,18,FMonarch - although in reality they
OL,19,Fwill never be used.
