OL,6,FTony Blair wrote in his memoirs that
OL,7,Fhe tripped on the carpet at this
OL,8,Fmoment and almost fell into the hands
OL,9,Fof Queen Elizabeth.
OL,11,FHaving accepted the "commission" to
OL,12,Fform a new government, the King and
OL,13,Fhis new prime minister will have a
OL,14,Fbrief exchange.
OL,16,FIf he wants it, Starmer can have a
OL,17,Fmoment in another room to collect his
OL,18,Fthoughts and make final adjustments to
OL,19,Fhis big speech, before being shown out
OL,20,Fby an equerry.
